#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 71. Bhāvanāsutta → bhāvanānuyuttasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.71:0.3"
msgid "71. Bhāvanāsutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.71:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Bhāvanaṃ ananuyuttassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:1.2"
msgid "‘aho vata me anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucceyyā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:1.3"
msgid "atha khvassa neva anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuccati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:1.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:1.5"
msgid "‘Abhāvitattā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:1.6"
msgid "Kissa abhāvitattā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:1.7"
msgid ""
"Catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ sammappadhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ, "
"pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ, pañcannaṃ balānaṃ, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ, ariyassa "
"aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.126"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.71:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni aṭṭha vā dasa vā dvādasa vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.2"
msgid ""
"Tānassu kukkuṭiyā na sammā adhisayitāni, na sammā pariseditāni, na sammā "
"paribhāvitāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.3"
msgid "Kiñcāpi tassā kukkuṭiyā evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata me kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā aṇḍakosaṃ "
"padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjeyyun’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.5"
msgid ""
"atha kho abhabbāva te kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā "
"aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjituṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.7"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni na sammā adhisayitāni, na sammā "
"pariseditāni, na sammā paribhāvitāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.8"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhāvanaṃ ananuyuttassa bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi "
"evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.9"
msgid "‘aho vata me anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucceyyā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.10"
msgid "atha khvassa neva anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuccati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.11"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.12"
msgid "‘Abhāvitattā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.13"
msgid "Kissa abhāvitattā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:2.14"
msgid ""
"Catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ sammappadhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ, "
"pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ, pañcannaṃ balānaṃ, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ, ariyassa "
"aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.71:3.1"
msgid ""
"Bhāvanaṃ anuyuttassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi na evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:3.2"
msgid "‘aho vata me anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucceyyā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:3.3"
msgid "atha khvassa anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuccati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:3.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:3.5"
msgid "‘Bhāvitattā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:3.6"
msgid "Kissa bhāvitattā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:3.7"
msgid ""
"Catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ sammappadhānānaṃ, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ, "
"pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ, pañcannaṃ balānaṃ, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ, ariyassa "
"aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.127"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.71:4.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni aṭṭha vā dasa vā dvādasa vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.2"
msgid ""
"Tānassu kukkuṭiyā sammā adhisayitāni, sammā pariseditāni, sammā "
"paribhāvitāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.3"
msgid "Kiñcāpi tassā kukkuṭiyā na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.4"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata me kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā aṇḍakosaṃ "
"padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjeyyun’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.5"
msgid ""
"atha kho bhabbāva te kukkuṭapotakā pādanakhasikhāya vā mukhatuṇḍakena vā "
"aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā sotthinā abhinibbhijjituṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.7"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi, bhikkhave, kukkuṭiyā aṇḍāni sammā adhisayitāni, sammā "
"pariseditāni, sammā paribhāvitāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.8"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhāvanaṃ anuyuttassa bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi na "
"evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.9"
msgid "‘aho vata me anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimucceyyā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.10"
msgid "atha khvassa anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuccati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.11"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.12"
msgid "‘Bhāvitattā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.13"
msgid "Kissa bhāvitattā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.71:4.14"
msgid "Catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ … pe … ariyassa aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: phalagaṇḍassa → palagaṇḍassa (bj, pts1) | phalabhaṇḍhassa (s1-3)
#. VAR: dissanteva → khīyante (mr)
#. VAR: aṅgulipadāni dissati → aṅgulapadāni dissanti aṅgulapadaṃ (ka-ma)
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="sc5"></a> VAR:[phalagaṇḍassa → palagaṇḍassa (bj, pts1) | phalabhaṇḍhassa (s1-3)] VAR:[dissanteva → khīyante (mr)] VAR:[aṅgulipadāni dissanti (s1, pts1)]
#. VAR: dissanti (s1, pts1)
msgctxt "an7.71:5.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, phalagaṇḍassa vā phalagaṇḍantevāsikassa vā dissanteva "
"vāsijaṭe aṅgulipadāni dissati aṅguṭṭhapadaṃ. No ca khvassa evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti: ‘"
"ettakaṃ me ajja vāsijaṭassa khīṇaṃ, ettakaṃ hiyyo, ettakaṃ pare’ti, atha "
"khvassa khīṇe ‘khīṇan’teva ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

# Here, as always, khina does not mean “destruction”.
msgctxt "an7.71:5.2"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhāvanaṃ anuyuttassa bhikkhuno viharato kiñcāpi na "
"evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti: ‘ettakaṃ me ajja āsavānaṃ khīṇaṃ, ettakaṃ hiyyo, ettakaṃ "
"pare’ti, atha khvassa khīṇe ‘khīṇan’teva ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: vettabandhanabaddhāya → vettabandhāya (mr)
#. VAR: parihāyanti → paṭippassambhanti (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an7.71:6.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, sāmuddikāya nāvāya vettabandhanabaddhāya cha māsāni "
"udake pariyādāya hemantikena thale ukkhittāya vātātapaparetāni bandhanāni, "
"tāni pāvussakena meghena abhippavuṭṭhāni appakasireneva parihāyanti, "
"pūtikāni bhavanti."
msgstr ""

# The use of patipassmbhati, and the variant verb in the previous sentence, are unusual.
msgctxt "an7.71:6.2"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhāvanaṃ anuyuttassa bhikkhuno viharato "
"appakasireneva saṃyojanāni paṭippassambhanti, pūtikāni bhavantī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.71:6.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
